text: My child on one fateful morning, once checked into the class, child was still crying, but that Chinese teacher just left him alone crying on the floor (still with his bag on his shoulder). I have a photo of it, uploading it will sure cause it to be viral. Unattended for a few minutes. That Chinese teacher kept saying "I have other children to look after" all the time.
A brilliant principal helming a centre full of astounding educators.
